import React from "react";
import { SignUpContainer ,
  SignUpHeading,
  SignUpForm,
  SignUpFormElement,
  SignUpFormSubmit,
  PersonalDetailsTitle
} from "./styles";
import Input from "../../neu-components/Input";
import Dropdown from "../../neu-components/Dropdown";

function SignUp(props) {
  return <SignUpContainer>
    <SignUpHeading>Sign Up</SignUpHeading>
    <SignUpForm>
      <SignUpFormElement>
        <Input label="Email"/>
      </SignUpFormElement>
      <SignUpFormElement>
        <Input label="Password"/>
      </SignUpFormElement>
      <SignUpFormElement>
        <Input label="Confirm Password"/>
      </SignUpFormElement>
      <SignUpFormElement>
      <PersonalDetailsTitle>Personal Details</PersonalDetailsTitle>
      </SignUpFormElement>
      <SignUpFormElement>
        <Input label="First Name"/>
      </SignUpFormElement>
      <SignUpFormElement>
        <Input label="Last Name"/>
      </SignUpFormElement>
      <SignUpFormElement>
        <Dropdown label="Gender"/>
      </SignUpFormElement>
      <SignUpFormElement>
        <Dropdown label="Language"/>
      </SignUpFormElement>
      <SignUpFormElement>
        <Input label="Phone Number"/>
      </SignUpFormElement>
    </SignUpForm>
  </SignUpContainer>;
}
export default SignUp;
